{"tid":1414254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 死仆街 ］董建華：近期事件是明目張膽的政治要脅","createTime":"2019-08-05T11:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:22:32.000Z","uid":39550,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2ee63145380ede920cb1782186b870c29456b9","tid":1414254,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國政協副主席董建華發表聲明 <br />\n<br />\n董建華指近期的暴力已無關修例爭議，而是明目張膽的政治要脅，公然挑戰中央政府權威，形容小部分暴徒用各種方式擾亂社會秩序，企圖綁架市民、癱瘓政府、脅迫中央、爭奪特區管治權，強調這些險惡的政治圖謀是不會得逞，國家主權不容侵犯，香港治安不容破壞。<br />\n<br />\n董建華表明全力支持以行政長官林鄭月娥為首的特區政府、依法治港以及警方嚴正執法，恢復社會安定繁榮，希望正義的市民站出來，向香港的害群之馬說不。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358055&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358055%26refer%3DShare&d=vE0XmFSztYUmu7sR0UJCJCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=9b93377d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358055%26refer%3DShare&h=e6a842f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358055&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"544fcf4b7ee2118e0239991b2b0f0a418071ff14","tid":1414254,"uid":39550,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港就係由哩條死仆街開始落後！死走狗！冚家落地獄！</span></span>"},{"pid":"93f4ec120f021b0241a80e3795ec6ee77a907da0","tid":1414254,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e610712dd437e0fd822f86a114d047e59425c5cd","tid":1414254,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:01:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"29c7cc56ff36bfe54c996ee1be58384f89c6c640","tid":1414254,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:02:11.000Z","msg":"凡是敵人&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\